est` to avoid Byte Buddy’s reflection-based injection path that requires `java.lang` opens.\n\nChange made:\n- Replaced `ClassLoadingStrategy.Default.INJECTION` with `ClassInjector.UsingUnsafe.ofSystemLoader().injectRaw(...)`\n- Temporarily sets `org.modelmapper.internal.bytebuddy.safe=false`\n- Restores the previous property value afterward\n- Keeps the fake `Installer` on the system class loader so `AgentBuilder.Default.resolveByteBuddyAgentInstrumentation()` still reaches the intended dynamic-access call sites\n\nUpdated file:\n\n- `tests/src/org.modelmapper/modelmapper/3.2.0/src/test/java/org_modelmapper/modelmapper/AgentBuilderInnerDefaultTest.java`\n\nI did not run the tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_01e59afe7f0611f70169fc204341d8819f82c3ff8372fd1da5\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1097, "output": 672, "cacheRead": 48128, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 49897, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778130998960, "responseId": "resp_01e59afe7f0611f70169fc2037c338819faf52863d1be49689"}, "toolResults": []}
