eletes any stale fake `Installer.class` previously written into test output\n- Keeps the explicit temporary `modelmapper` module and driver module\n- The driver now targets a named installer module that `modelmapper` should not initially read, forcing `AgentBuilder.Default.resolveByteBuddyAgentInstrumentation()` to invoke `Module.addReads(...)`\n\nUpdated file:\n\n- `tests/src/org.modelmapper/modelmapper/3.2.0/src/test/java/org_modelmapper/modelmapper/AgentBuilderInnerDefaultTest.java`\n\nI did not run the tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_01e59afe7f0611f70169fc23b2af6c819f84ddc3e7fd665066\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1683, "output": 784, "cacheRead": 77312, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 79779, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778131877427, "responseId": "resp_01e59afe7f0611f70169fc23a64b64819f878260afff36448d"}, "toolResults": []}
